12.title: Sunny's No Jam Vlogs
12.plot: Hello, everyone. Today, we went to Coney Island in Brooklyn. I really enjoyed editing this vlog. It gives off so much summer beach/summer sunset/summer night vibes. Love it. Kate has her own website, so if you like photos, go check it out at 1. See you around.

13.title: K-Pop Idol EXID's Hani L.I.E Showcase Makeup Tutorial
13.plot: Hola, everyone!. It's Sunny here. Today, I have a super exciting video for you all. I got the amazing opportunity to collab with Glossy Days to launch my own little pouch. YAS!!. I'm so happy!!. In the pouch that was designed (half designed) by me, there are going to be five items that I tried and tested. I picked the best six that I highly recommend and put it in the pouch.

14.title: Holy Grail: Orange Lipsticks
14.plot: Hey, everyone. This is Sunny. Today, I'll be sharing with you guys my favorite orange lipsticks. I'm so excited to start this series and show you guys some of my holy grail products. So, hope you enjoy this video. 18.plot: Hi, everyone. It's Sunny here. The makeup look I'll be showing you guys today is a Summer-to-Fall, Gold Leaves Makeup. (That makes no sense, I know.) 22.title: Red Velvet's Joy 'Russian Roulette' Cover Makeup Tutorial
22.plot: Hey, everyone. It's Sunny here. Today, I have a new K-pop cover makeup tutorial for you guys. Today's makeup is inspired by Red Velvet's new \"Russian Roulette\" album. I decided to do Joy's makeup.\nThis album concept is so cute. Joy is seriously rocking the blonde hair and the short fringe.\nEnjoy the tutorial.

I made this video to let you guys know and also to show y'all/recommend some lip tints I got for myself. Here is the list: beautynetkorea.com (bought all of the products in this video from here.); ibuybeauti.com (I come to this site so often. ...

24.title: BLACK HIGHLIGHTER: Let's Try It Out!
24.plot: Hello, everyone. It's Sunny here. Today's video includes lots of excitement, so beware. Let's open up the new Jeffree Star Black Highlighter together. As a person who really loves Jeffree Star cosmetics, I wanted to try this out on camera for the first time. I'm pretty much never going to use it again - Please share with me in the comments how I should use it.
